sequenceDiagram
    actor Client as Клиент
    participant UI as React Frontend
    participant RepairController as RepairController
    participant RepairService as RepairService
    participant StatusRepo as StatusRepository
    participant RepairRepo as RepairRequestRepository
    participant DB as Database
    Client->>UI: Заполняет форму ремонта
    UI->>RepairController: POST /api/repairs
    RepairController->>RepairService: createRepairRequest(request, user)
    RepairService->>StatusRepo: Найти начальный статус REPAIR
    StatusRepo->>DB: SELECT statuses
    DB-->>StatusRepo: Статус Принята
    RepairService->>RepairRepo: Сохранить заявку
    RepairRepo->>DB: INSERT repair_requests
    DB-->>RepairRepo: Заявка создана
    RepairService-->>RepairController: RepairRequestDto
    RepairController-->>UI: 201 Created
    UI-->>Client: Заявка отправлена
